title: Energy.Cycle.Collectors.Edition-PROPHET
description:
Energy Cycle Collector's Edition (c) Sometimes You

release date: August 2769
protection: Steam
# of discs: 1
languages: EN

Energy Cycle new puzzle game from the developers
of Energy Balance. When you click each cell on the
game field - it changes color, and the colors of
adjacent cells horizontally and vertically. Your
task to bring all the cells to the same color
Sounds pretty easy, but try to do it!

This release includes bonus content:

* Artbook "How we made art for Energy Cycle"
* Pack of exclusive "Energy Cycle" wallpapers
* Random memories (Photo album)
* Soundtrack

1- Unpack, burn or mount
2- Install the game
3- Copy the cracked content from PROPHET dir
4- Go To Hell!

NOTE:
The game is updated to v1.04
